replies.author: ItIsEnderman
replies.txt_content:
（Ic2c extras）该MOD为工业时代2经典版（IC2C）添加了一些类似工业时代2实验版（IC2）的机器。
https://www.mcmod.cn/class/2180.html
（Ic2c extras）This mod is an addon to Ic2 Classic adding a few and items including ones based off ic2 experimental items while sticking to the ic2 classic theme. This mod WILL NOT WORK with ic2 experimental.
https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ic2c-extras

画蛇添足，请删除IC2 CLASSIC 和Ic2c extras这两个mod。
